&lt;div id="outline-container-sec-2" class="outline-2"&gt;
&lt;h2 id="sec-2"&gt;&lt;span class="section-number-2"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; Tabulating the results in column mode&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
We can use column view to see the results in a tabular like form. For example, here we capture the VOLUME and TOTAL&lt;sub&gt;ENERGY&lt;/sub&gt; properties.
&lt;/p&gt;

